title: Tangerous - DEMOlition: Tangerous (FLAC)
description:
In 2007, a mate of mine released a demo of his band&#039;s work. He&#039;s a ska-punk kind of guy, so expect sounds like that of RX Bandits.

I had joined this band, Tangerous, when it was under a different name, but I left due to personal musical conflicts. It&#039;s not quite my cup of tea, but some of you might like it.

Try it out, folks. If you don&#039;t like it, junk it. If you do, they&#039;re working on a full length album to be released this fall. Distribute to whomever you want.

--Yzou
